{"tid":1701722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"十一月最大嘅香港國際體壇盛事，點解無人提？","createTime":"2019-11-09T08:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T09:07:30.000Z","uid":277511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c88738108d81a2d48eb5ce5a491b14b2e7ed38ed","tid":1701722,"uid":277511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T08:58:00.000Z","msg":"第61屆「香港高爾夫球公開賽」將於11月28日至12月1日喺環境優美嘅<strong>權貴基地</strong>粉嶺香港哥爾夫球會內隆重舉行。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thehongkongopen.com/zh/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthehongkongopen.com%2Fzh%2F%20&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOKjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=b4f93fed\" target=\"_blank\">https://thehongkongopen.com/zh/ </a><br />\n我明白大家今日心情沉重，點解重要喺度向連登仔推介？<br />\n<br />\n抵玩 &ndash; 叫得公開賽即係平民百姓都可以入場參觀。頭兩日仲係免費。呢Ｄ高貴私人地方，平時只招待會員。邊個係會員？<strong>咩瘤呀，十一呀，荷蘭呀</strong>，白頭呀都好似係，自己查啦。<br />\n<br />\n安全 &ndash; 高爾夫球號稱＜君子的運動＞，非暴力的象徵，連登仔多Ｄ接觸呢Ｄ活動，咪可以止暴制亂。呢Ｄ高貴私人地方，梗係<strong>唔會容許</strong>有ＴＧ，pepper spray同popo呢Ｄ場面。<br />\n<br />\n國際關注 &ndash; 這是歐洲巡迴賽的第一站，國際體壇媒體會<strong>大幅報導</strong>。高爾夫球在外國政要公司高層之間，關注程度<strong>重勁過NBA</strong>!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.europeantour.com/european-tour/honma-hong-kong-open-presented-by-amundi-2019/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europeantour.com%2Feuropean-tour%2Fhonma-hong-kong-open-presented-by-amundi-2019%2F%20&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOKjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=2dd707a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.europeantour.com/european-tour/honma-hong-kong-open-presented-by-amundi-2019/ </a><br />\n<br />\n不過呢，參觀還參觀，你哋千祈要守規矩。同足球籃球欖球呢Ｄ暴力運動唔同，高爾夫球既特点係要<strong>絕對肅靜不受任何干擾 </strong>&ndash; 球員打球時，要非常專注，旁觀者不要說談話，就是咳嗽都不可以。<strong>夢遊口号呀激光呀標語呀</strong>就更加唔得。球會外面都唔好!<br />\n<br />\n高爾夫球既另一特点係球場同參觀區<strong>非常接近同冇明顯分隔</strong>。大家知粉嶺球會<strong>成個荃灣</strong>咁大 ，球會附近重有馬路<strong>高層</strong>屋苑，個幾日只靠數百義工維持秩序。即係話，比賽要順利進行，非常<strong>依靠觀眾同週邊居民自律</strong>。參賽Ｄ國際球星身驕肉貴，身家億億聲，贏輸幾球美金上落，有咩事不單止你地賠唔起，特區政府都會大失面子，外國媒體仲會<strong>大肆報導</strong>！<br />\n<br />\n相反，大家幫手做得好好睇睇，就可以<strong>幫球會同Ｄ會員向政府邀功</strong>，&ldquo;睇下我地做到野幫你攪番埸盛事&rdquo;挽回分數，大條道理<strong>司法覆核挑戰收地</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n識做啦？"},{"pid":"603d5301a6892c9428c1583b230e53566fee3cd2","tid":1701722,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gb0BsVw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgb0BsVw.jpg&h=f2aff6e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總部: <a href=\"http://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielamgroup&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOKjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=93c67c17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup</a><br />\n<br />\n九龍西分區: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DRSKGRrfozKTM3at-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLC07DRSKGRrfozKTM3at-A&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOKjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=008eb549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DRSKGRrfozKTM3at-A</a><br />\n九龍東分區: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FKjJ1BKLLTBC6hFo0ZwLxw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFKjJ1BKLLTBC6hFo0ZwLxw&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOKjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=71e15849\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FKjJ1BKLLTBC6hFo0ZwLxw</a><br />\n新界東分區: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DRKBT8rgAIkf-Z1FjQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLC07DRKBT8rgAIkf-Z1FjQ&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOKjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=346fb5e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DRKBT8rgAIkf-Z1FjQ</a><br />\n新界西北分區: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DRdHq8ifSxipZNMNFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLC07DRdHq8ifSxipZNMNFA&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOKjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=3f9c5524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DRdHq8ifSxipZNMNFA</a><br />\n港島西分區: <br />\n<a h